2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6.5 alias 사용</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dept_id<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> d<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> s_emp e<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> s_dept d\n<span class=\"token keyword\">where</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dept_id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> d<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"65\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#65\" aria-label=\"65 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6.5</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>서울 지역에 근무하는 사원에 대해 각 사원의 이름과 근무하는 부서명을 나타내시오</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> 사원명<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> r<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> 지역명<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> d<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> 부서명\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> s_emp e<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> s_dept d<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> s_region r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">where</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dept_id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> d<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id\n<span class=\"token operator\">and</span> d<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>region_id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> r<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id\n<span class=\"token operator\">and</span> r<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">order</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">by</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"66\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#66\" aria-label=\"66 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6.6</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>non-equijoin 각 사원의 이름과 급여등급을 나타내시오</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>salary<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> g<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>grade 급여등급\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> s_emp e<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> salgrade g\n<span class=\"token keyword\">where</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>salary <span class=\"token operator\">between</span> g<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>losal <span class=\"token operator\">and</span> g<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>hisal\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"67\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#67\" aria-label=\"67 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6.7</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>outer join 이름, 사번, 담당고객 이름. 단, 고객에 대하여 담당영업사원이 없더라도 모든 고객의 이름을 나타내고, 사번순으로 오름차순 정렬</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> c<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> s_emp e<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> s_customer c\n<span class=\"token keyword\">where</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> c<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>sales_rep_id <span class=\"token comment\">-- (+)를 빼면?</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">--where e.id = c.sales_rep_id (+) -- (+)위치를 바꾸면?</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">order</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">by</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"68-self-join\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#68-self-join\" aria-label=\"68 self join permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6.8 self join</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> w<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id 사번<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> w<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name 사원명<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> m<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id 부서장사번<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> m<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name 부서장명\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> s_emp w<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> s_emp m\n<span class=\"token keyword\">where</span> w<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>manager_id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> m<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id\n<span class=\"token keyword\">order</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">by</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"68\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#68\" aria-label=\"68 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6.8</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>self join 직원중에 ‘김정미’와 같은 직책을 가지는 사원의 이름과 직책, 급여, 부서번호를 나타내시오</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">select</span> e1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> e1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>title<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> e1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>dept_id\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> s_emp e1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> s_emp e2\n<span class=\"token keyword\">where</span> e1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>title <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> e2<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>title\n<span class=\"token operator\">and</span> e2<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'김정미'</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">and</span> e1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;></span> <span class=\"token string\">'김정미'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">order</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">by</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<